      "writtenOn": "2019-01-08T23:28:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t like the idea of padding it, no we\u0027re never going to have 6 figures of instances of one type, but I don\u0027t like introducing arbitrary limitations like that. If someone asks \"why\u0027s it called gce-trusty-000001\" it seems weird to answer \"because it makes the code easier to write\", especially because it makes talking about the Swarming bot itself more annoying. I\u0027d prefer to just query over 5000 entities at that point.\n\nI\u0027ll do the secondary index-less query for now, it can always be revised later.",
